.B
\fBpkix_is_fixed_dh_cert(Cert) -> boolean() when Cert :: cert().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Checks if a certificate is a fixed Diffie-Hellman certificate.


.RE
.B
\fBpkix_is_issuer(CertorCRL, IssuerCert) -> boolean()\fR
\fB                        when\fR
\fB                            CertorCRL :: cert() | #'CertificateList'{},\fR
\fB                            IssuerCert :: cert().\fR

